Subject: Link-me trial follow up survey

<h4>Dear [% firstname -%]</h4>

<p>Thank you for taking part in Link-me. Because you have been part of the trial for about X months now, we are interested to hear how things have been going for you. Your next Link-me survey is available for you to complete here.</p>

<p>We have tried it out with people and found that the survey takes around 15 minutes to complete. </p>

<p>All of the information you give us in this survey is strictly confidential, and your responses will help us to find out how best to help people find the right care for their mental health.</p>

<p>INSTRUCTIONS</p>

<p><ol>
  <li>This survey asks about you, your health service use and lifestyle. It is private, and your answers are confidential.</li>
  <li>Try to answer each question – even if they look alike.</li>
  <li>There are no right or wrong answers – just give the best answer you can.</li>
</ol></p>

<p>If you have any questions about the trial, please contact us at <a href="mailto:link-me@unimelb.edu.au.">link-me@unimelb.edu.au.</a>.</p>

<p>Thank you for your time and help.</p>

<p>The Link-me team</p>



